						<div class="postbody">I wonder whether the breakpoint condition is being interpreted as &quot;break when there's a write to $4011 and $4011 contains $FF&quot;.<br /><br />The hardware sweep sounds no different than manually setting the channel period, aside from it not resetting the phase when the high byte is modified. If you want to hear sweeps, just listen to sound effects.</div>

